OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,7,FRollins has died at the age of 95.
OL,9,FThe renowned musician, known as the
OL,10,F"saxophone colossus" due to his
OL,11,Fimprovisational skill, had a prolific
OL,12,Fcareer spanning more than 50 years.
OL,14,FHe died on Monday at his home in
OL,15,FWoodstock, New York, where he had been
OL,16,Flargely housebound over the past
OL,17,Fcouple of years due to various
OL,18,Fphysical problems, his spokesperson
OL,19,FTerri Hinte said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
