CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FDespite his enduring success, Rollins
OL,7,Fwas never quite satisfied with his art
OL,8,Fand occasionally took lengthy hiatuses
OL,9,Ffrom playing.
OL,11,FAt the peak of his popularity, Rollins
OL,12,Fwent into seclusion, spending two
OL,13,Fyears practising alone on a solitary
OL,14,Fniche above the East River on a
OL,15,FWilliamsburg Bridge walkway.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,F"The thing that I am most proud of in
OL,7,Fmy career is the fact that I was able
OL,8,Fto see beyond being popular and all
OL,9,Fthat stuff and do what my inner self
OL,10,Ftold me to do," Rollins told AP in
OL,11,F2007.
OL,13,FRollins got his first major break when
OL,14,Fhe was invited to join Thelonious
OL,15,FMonk's band in his late teens, and was
OL,16,Fintroduced to the recording world
OL,17,Fbefore he finished high school.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FBut his rising star almost faded when
OL,7,Fhe became hooked on heroin at the age
OL,8,Fof 19, which led to two short stints
OL,9,Fin jail in 1950 and 1953.
OL,11,FRollins then found himself living on
OL,12,Fthe streets in Chicago. In 1954, he
OL,13,Fchecked himself into a hospital in
OL,14,FLexington to undergo drug treatment,
OL,15,Fwhich he said gave him a spiritual
OL,16,Fawakening.
OL,18,F"I began to have a deeper philosophy
OL,19,Fof what life was about. From that
OL,20,Fpoint on is when my consciousness
OL,21,Fawoke," Rollins would later say.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
