PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FAfter being discharged, he returned to
OL,7,FChicago and signed on as a member of
OL,8,Fthe Max Roach-Clifford Brown quintet,
OL,9,Fand in 1956, he recorded the solo
OL,10,Falbum Saxophone Colossus, which
OL,11,Fremains one of his most influential
OL,12,Fworks.
OL,14,FIn the following two years, Rollins
OL,15,Ftook a different approach, switching
OL,16,Fto a pianoless trio on three more
OL,17,Flandmark albums: Way Out West, A Night
OL,18,Fat the Village Vanguard and Freedom
OL,19,FSuite.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FHe then took a hiatus and returned to
OL,7,Fthe scene in 1961, where he embraced a
OL,8,Fdifferent sound - a move that divided
OL,9,Fhis fans.
OL,11,FIn the mid-60s, Rollins toured heavily
OL,12,Fin Europe, switching back and forth
OL,13,Fbetween more traditional and avant-
OL,14,Fgarde approaches, and he contributed
OL,15,Foriginal music to the soundtrack of
OL,16,Fthe 1966 British movie Alfie.
OL,18,FIt was during a trip to Japan when
OL,19,FRollins discovered Zen Buddhism,
OL,20,Fprompting another lengthy sabbatical
OL,21,Fthat would last into the early 1970s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
