PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FIn the 1990s and 2000s, Rollins
OL,7,Freleased a string of critically
OL,8,Facclaimed albums, and he continued to
OL,9,Ftour into his 80s.
OL,11,FGrammy-winning song Why Was I Born was
OL,12,Ffrom the album Without a Song: The 9/
OL,13,F11 Concert, a live recording from a
OL,14,Fperformance in Boston just four days
OL,15,Fafter the September 11 attacks.
OL,17,FRollins had been evacuated from his
OL,18,Fapartment a few blocks away from the
OL,19,FWorld Trade Center and had done the
OL,20,Fconcert at the urging of his wife and
OL,21,Fmanager, Lucille.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
