PN,31510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1779833501
OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FThe album was released after her death
OL,7,Fin 2004.
OL,9,FIn 2011, Rollins became the eighth
OL,10,Fjazz musician to be recognised with
OL,11,FKennedy Center Honors in a ceremony
OL,12,Falongside actress Meryl Streep.
OL,14,FRollins was later forced into
OL,15,Fretirement by pulmonary fibrosis, a
OL,16,Fthickening and damaging of the lungs,
OL,17,Fand he played his last concert in 2012
OL,18,Fbefore stopping altogether in 2014.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
