OL,3,CLegendary jazz saxophonist Sonny
OL,4,CRollins dies aged 95
OL,6,FHe is survived by his nephew Clifton
OL,7,FAnderson and nieces Vallyn Anderson
OL,8,Fand Gabrielle DeGroat.
